name: Threads Gift Card - $25
description:
Threads Gift Card - $25

Not sure what to get that special someone? Give the gift of options! Gift cards are usable at our retail location, 108 Laurens Street SW, or at our online store. 

Shipping for gift cards purchased online only costs $1! Please, order in advance if needed by a certain date, as gift cards are shipped First Class via USPS, which takes approx. 3 business days. 

<b>Note: If you are shipping directly to the gift recipient, please include the receipts name ( ex. To: Jane Doe ) and a salutation ( ex. Love, Mom & Dad )  in the "comments" section when you check out.
